Here is a list of arabic vocabulary. I will ask you for one of these things:

1. To provide 10 short, SIMPLE sentences using ONLY these words. The sentences should be in the present tense and only use the singular person. Include all vocalizations, vowel markers, and ending markers. Include the translation of these in a separate section so I can practice trying to translate them myself before seeing the answer

2. To provide some questions where you give me a bunch of Arabic letters in individual form and I will try to connect them (to practice their connected forms). Just list the problems with numbers, no need for any intro or explanatory text. Underneath the practice problems, please put in the answers. Please include hamzas in half of the problems, either as individual letters, or when it's used with kursis.

3. To provide 3 individual words randomly chosen from the following list. Do not include the translation of the words. Only output Arabic. Output them in the form "<word>. <word>. <word>. ..."

